Results and Discussion

The developed application successfully classifies passwords into three categories:

Weak Passwords

Passwords with short length and limited character diversity are classified as weak.

Medium Passwords

Passwords containing a combination of letters and numbers but lacking advanced complexity are classified as medium.

Strong Passwords

Passwords containing uppercase letters, lowercase letters, digits, special characters, and sufficient length are classified as strong.

The system provides immediate feedback and recommendations, helping users improve password quality.

